  <brief_title>Comparison of Self and Clinician Administered Rating Scales in Patients With ADHD</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Self and Clinician Administered Rating Scales in Patients With Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
