  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective is to establish the concurrent validity of the clinician administered
      Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder-Rating Scale (ADHD-RS) and the patient administered
      Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder Self Report Scale (ASRS) v1.1 Symptom Checklist.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
